they told me?

15:17.651 --> 15:21.486
They told me that the real
troublemaker here is you.

15:21.488 --> 15:24.188
Get off my back.
It's none of your beeswax.

15:24.190 --> 15:26.291
Oh, it is my beeswax.

15:26.293 --> 15:29.027
It is very much
my beeswax, dad.

15:29.995 --> 15:31.462
I am responsible for you.

15:31.464 --> 15:33.698
