- No, she's not.

16:54.781 --> 16:58.149
But I plan on seeing her
very, very shortly.

16:58.151 --> 17:00.752
Awesome. Tell her
little gonzalo says hi.

17:00.754 --> 17:02.286
She'll know
what that means.

17:02.288 --> 17:03.788
I'm sure she will.

