18:09.756 --> 18:12.090
I'll take it.

18:17.096 --> 18:19.597
Nobody tells you how
to parent your parents.

18:19.599 --> 18:21.566
Yeah, it's tough, man.

18:21.568 --> 18:24.535
It's a very difficult age.

18:24.537 --> 18:29.107
